{"tid":2386307,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"劉慧卿：接獲不少公務員查詢，擔心宣誓後影響BNO移民","createTime":"2021-01-29T13:21:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-29T13:57:06.000Z","uid":5195,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4c815156337cccd3a8a17fe18831b981cb8af62e","tid":2386307,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T13:21:58.000Z","msg":"劉慧卿：盼中方冷靜應對BNO事宜　讓港人自行選擇<br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部表示，中方星期日起不再承認BNO作為旅行證件和身份證明，並保留採取進一步措施的權利。一直關注BNO議題的民主黨前主席劉慧卿指出，措施暫時對香港人沒有太大的影響，希望中國政府能冷靜、心平氣和應對，讓香港人自行作選擇，不要作加辣措施。劉慧卿重申，中國政府多年來都不承認BNO作為旅行證件，不用再重申立場，又說，當局一再強調不承認BNO的地位，<span class=\"red\">理論上民主黨另一名前主席胡志偉應可獲釋。</span><br />\n<br />\n劉慧卿表示，<span class=\"red\">接獲不少公務員查詢，擔心簽署宣誓聲明後會影響透過BNO簽證申請居留</span>，她已向英國政府查詢和反映擔憂，暫時未獲回覆，相信英國方面好快會有回覆。<br />\n<br />\n2021-01-29 21:10:14<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8a6d1afc5a1a57ec4508cdac0cc4fbcefcb9eef","tid":2386307,"uid":53612,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T13:24:53.000Z","msg":"加速師一條直路"},{"pid":"24a21240fdaeb095ccea39cf88067422073b1772","tid":2386307,"uid":389613,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T13:27:14.000Z","msg":"唔撚驚就 MPF 回水啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔撚驚就比 BNO 出入境啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔撚驚就唔逼人宣勢啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔撚驚就堂堂正正留人啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dbb965e9cadfea6f7dcceebb6715871c0214977","tid":2386307,"uid":212623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T13:28:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f475c1117190ff7078331aeaa190907232dc